    "title": "IBM India International Enterprises is Hiring: Full Stack Developer (Lead)",
    "description": "IBM India International Enterprises has an exciting opening for a Full Stack Developer at our Ghaziabad office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout IBM India International Enterprises:\nIBM India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Life and accident insurance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IBM India International Enterprises!",
